{
  "video_id": "ziGD7vQOwl8",
  "title": "The unheard story of David and Goliath | Malcolm Gladwell",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12536.0,
      "end_time": 13819.0,
      "text": "So I wanted to tell a story"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 13819.0,
      "end_time": 17291.0,
      "text": "that really obsessed me when I was writing my new book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17291.0,
      "end_time": 20838.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s a story of something that happened"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20838.0,
      "end_time": 22411.0,
      "text": "3,000 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22411.0,
      "end_time": 25638.0,
      "text": "when the Kingdom of Israel was in its infancy."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25638.0,
      "end_time": 28370.0,
      "text": "And it takes place in an area called the Shephelah"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28370.0,
      "end_time": 30700.0,
      "text": "in what is now Israel."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30700.0,
      "end_time": 32948.0,
      "text": "And the reason the story obsessed me is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32948.0,
      "end_time": 36034.0,
      "text": "I thought I understood it, and then I went back over it"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36034.0,
      "end_time": 40140.0,
      "text": "and I realized that I didn&#39;t understand it at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40140.0,
      "end_time": 44957.0,
      "text": "Ancient Palestine had a -- along its eastern border,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44957.0,
      "end_time": 46273.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a mountain range."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46273.0,
      "end_time": 48132.0,
      "text": "Still same is true of Israel today."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48132.0,
      "end_time": 51065.0,
      "text": "And in the mountain range are all of the ancient cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51065.0,
      "end_time": 55523.0,
      "text": "of that region, so Jerusalem, Bethlehem, Hebron."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55523.0,
      "end_time": 57748.0,
      "text": "And then there&#39;s a coastal plain"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57748.0,
      "end_time": 61103.0,
      "text": "along the Mediterranean, where Tel Aviv is now."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61103.0,
      "end_time": 64503.0,
      "text": "And connecting the mountain range with the coastal plain"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64503.0,
      "end_time": 66436.0,
      "text": "is an area called the Shephelah,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66436.0,
      "end_time": 70855.0,
      "text": "which is a series of valleys and ridges that run east to west,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70855.0,
      "end_time": 74034.0,
      "text": "and you can follow the Shephelah, go through the Shephelah"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74034.0,
      "end_time": 76787.0,
      "text": "to get from the coastal plain to the mountains."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76787.0,
      "end_time": 78481.0,
      "text": "And the Shephelah, if you&#39;ve been to Israel, you&#39;ll know"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78481.0,
      "end_time": 80889.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s just about the most beautiful part of Israel."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 80889.0,
      "end_time": 83807.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s gorgeous, with forests of oak"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 83807.0,
      "end_time": 86222.0,
      "text": "and wheat fields and vineyards."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 86222.0,
      "end_time": 89601.0,
      "text": "But more importantly, though, in the history of that region,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 89601.0,
      "end_time": 93366.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s served, it&#39;s had a real strategic function,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 93366.0,
      "end_time": 96279.0,
      "text": "and that is, it is the means by which hostile armies"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 96279.0,
      "end_time": 98862.0,
      "text": "on the coastal plain find their way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 98862.0,
      "end_time": 102484.0,
      "text": "get up into the mountains and threaten those living in the mountains."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 102484.0,
      "end_time": 105511.0,
      "text": "And 3,000 years ago, that&#39;s exactly what happens."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 105511.0,
      "end_time": 109788.0,
      "text": "The Philistines, who are the biggest of enemies"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 109788.0,
      "end_time": 111290.0,
      "text": "of the Kingdom of Israel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 111290.0,
      "end_time": 113002.0,
      "text": "are living in the coastal plain."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 113002.0,
      "end_time": 116298.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re originally from Crete. They&#39;re a seafaring people."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 116298.0,
      "end_time": 118721.0,
      "text": "And they may start to make their way"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 118721.0,
      "end_time": 120961.0,
      "text": "through one of the valleys of the Shephelah"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 120961.0,
      "end_time": 122128.0,
      "text": "up into the mountains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 122128.0,
      "end_time": 124384.0,
      "text": "because what they want to do is occupy the highland area"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 124384.0,
      "end_time": 128385.0,
      "text": "right by Bethlehem and split the Kingdom of Israel in two."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 128384.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131650.0,
      "text": "And the Kingdom of Israel, which is headed by King Saul,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 131650.0,
      "end_time": 133383.0,
      "text": "obviously catches wind of this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 133383.0,
      "end_time": 136252.0,
      "text": "and Saul brings his army down from the mountains"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 136252.0,
      "end_time": 139907.0,
      "text": "and he confronts the Philistines in the Valley of Elah,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 139907.0,
      "end_time": 142365.0,
      "text": "one of the most beautiful of the valleys of the Shephelah."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 142365.0,
      "end_time": 145233.0,
      "text": "And the Israelites dig in along the northern ridge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 145233.0,
      "end_time": 149490.0,
      "text": "and the Philistines dig in along the southern ridge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 149490.0,
      "end_time": 152225.0,
      "text": "and the two armies just sit there for weeks"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 152225.0,
      "end_time": 154347.0,
      "text": "and stare at each other, because they&#39;re deadlocked."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 154347.0,
      "end_time": 156820.0,
      "text": "Neither can attack the other, because to attack the other side"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 156820.0,
      "end_time": 160076.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve got to come down the mountain into the valley"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 160076.0,
      "end_time": 162593.0,
      "text": "and then up the other side, and you&#39;re completely exposed."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 162593.0,
      "end_time": 164785.0,
      "text": "So finally, to break the deadlock,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 164785.0,
      "end_time": 167999.0,
      "text": "the Philistines send their mightiest warrior"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 167999.0,
      "end_time": 170476.0,
      "text": "down into the valley floor, and he calls out"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 170476.0,
      "end_time": 171932.0,
      "text": "and he says to the Israelites,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 171932.0,
      "end_time": 174560.0,
      "text": "&quot;Send your mightiest warrior down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 174560.0,
      "end_time": 176567.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;ll have this out, just the two of us.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 176567.0,
      "end_time": 180402.0,
      "text": "This was a tradition in ancient warfare called single combat."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 180402.0,
      "end_time": 182197.0,
      "text": "It was a way of settling disputes"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 182197.0,
      "end_time": 186321.0,
      "text": "without incurring the bloodshed of a major battle."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 186321.0,
      "end_time": 189281.0,
      "text": "And the Philistine who is sent down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 189281.0,
      "end_time": 191448.0,
      "text": "their mighty warrior, is a giant."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 191448.0,
      "end_time": 193223.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s 6 foot 9."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 193223.0,
      "end_time": 197936.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s outfitted head to toe in this glittering bronze armor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 197936.0,
      "end_time": 200995.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s got a sword and he&#39;s got a javelin"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 200995.0,
      "end_time": 203723.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s got his spear. He is absolutely terrifying."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 203723.0,
      "end_time": 208213.0,
      "text": "And he&#39;s so terrifying that none of the Israelite soldiers want to fight him."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 208213.0,
      "end_time": 212848.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a death wish, right? There&#39;s no way they think they can take him."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 212848.0,
      "end_time": 215141.0,
      "text": "And finally the only person who will come forward"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 215141.0,
      "end_time": 217652.0,
      "text": "is this young shepherd boy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 217652.0,
      "end_time": 220330.0,
      "text": "and he goes up to Saul and he says, &quot;I&#39;ll fight him.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 220330.0,
      "end_time": 223448.0,
      "text": "And Saul says, &quot;You can&#39;t fight him. That&#39;s ridiculous."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 223448.0,
      "end_time": 225770.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re this kid. This is this mighty warrior.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 225770.0,
      "end_time": 228193.0,
      "text": "But the shepherd is adamant. He says, &quot;No, no, no,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 228193.0,
      "end_time": 231186.0,
      "text": "you don&#39;t understand, I have been defending my flock"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 231186.0,
      "end_time": 235355.0,
      "text": "against lions and wolves for years. I think I can do it.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 235355.0,
      "end_time": 238569.0,
      "text": "And Saul has no choice. He&#39;s got no one else who&#39;s come forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 238569.0,
      "end_time": 239910.0,
      "text": "So he says, &quot;All right.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 239910.0,
      "end_time": 241122.0,
      "text": "And then he turns to the kid, and he says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 241122.0,
      "end_time": 244816.0,
      "text": "&quot;But you&#39;ve got to wear this armor. You can&#39;t go as you are.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 244816.0,
      "end_time": 247219.0,
      "text": "So he tries to give the shepherd his armor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 247219.0,
      "end_time": 248470.0,
      "text": "and the shepherd says, &quot;No.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 248470.0,
      "end_time": 250883.0,
      "text": "He says, &quot;I can&#39;t wear this stuff.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 250883.0,
      "end_time": 254957.0,
      "text": "The Biblical verse is, &quot;I cannot wear this for I have not proved it,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 254957.0,
      "end_time": 258134.0,
      "text": "meaning, &quot;I&#39;ve never worn armor before. You&#39;ve got to be crazy.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 258134.0,
      "end_time": 260740.0,
      "text": "So he reaches down instead on the ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 260740.0,
      "end_time": 262495.0,
      "text": "and picks up five stones"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 262495.0,
      "end_time": 264956.0,
      "text": "and puts them in his shepherd&#39;s bag"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 264956.0,
      "end_time": 269468.0,
      "text": "and starts to walk down the mountainside to meet the giant."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 269468.0,
      "end_time": 271674.0,
      "text": "And the giant sees this figure approaching,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 271674.0,
      "end_time": 274817.0,
      "text": "and calls out, &quot;Come to me so I can feed your flesh"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 274817.0,
      "end_time": 278794.0,
      "text": "to the birds of the heavens and the beasts of the field.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 278794.0,
      "end_time": 282229.0,
      "text": "He issues this kind of taunt towards this person"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 282229.0,
      "end_time": 283964.0,
      "text": "coming to fight him."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 283964.0,
      "end_time": 287310.0,
      "text": "And the shepherd draws closer and closer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 287310.0,
      "end_time": 290298.0,
      "text": "and the giant sees that he&#39;s carrying a staff."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 290298.0,
      "end_time": 291470.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s all he&#39;s carrying."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 291470.0,
      "end_time": 293338.0,
      "text": "Instead of a weapon, just this shepherd&#39;s staff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 293338.0,
      "end_time": 295910.0,
      "text": "and he says -- he&#39;s insulted --"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 295910.0,
      "end_time": 299267.0,
      "text": "&quot;Am I a dog that you would come to me with sticks?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 299267.0,
      "end_time": 302330.0,
      "text": "And the shepherd boy takes one of his stones"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 302330.0,
      "end_time": 305570.0,
      "text": "out of his pocket, puts it in his sling"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 305570.0,
      "end_time": 307865.0,
      "text": "and rolls it around and lets it fly"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 307865.0,
      "end_time": 310266.0,
      "text": "and it hits the giant right between the eyes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 310266.0,
      "end_time": 312364.0,
      "text": "right here, in his most vulnerable spot --"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 312364.0,
      "end_time": 315685.0,
      "text": "and he falls down either dead or unconscious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 315685.0,
      "end_time": 318179.0,
      "text": "and the shepherd boy runs up and takes his sword"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 318179.0,
      "end_time": 319865.0,
      "text": "and cuts off his head,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 319865.0,
      "end_time": 325416.0,
      "text": "and the Philistines see this and they turn and they just run."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 325416.0,
      "end_time": 329777.0,
      "text": "And of course, the name of the giant is Goliath"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 329777.0,
      "end_time": 332306.0,
      "text": "and the name of the shepherd boy is David,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 332306.0,
      "end_time": 335436.0,
      "text": "and the reason that story has obsessed me"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 335436.0,
      "end_time": 336874.0,
      "text": "over the course of writing my book"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 336874.0,
      "end_time": 339966.0,
      "text": "is that everything I thought I knew about that story"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 339966.0,
      "end_time": 342717.0,
      "text": "turned out to be wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 342717.0,
      "end_time": 346505.0,
      "text": "So David, in that story, is supposed to be the underdog, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 346505.0,
      "end_time": 348642.0,
      "text": "In fact, that term, David and Goliath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 348642.0,
      "end_time": 351623.0,
      "text": "has entered our language as a metaphor for"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 351623.0,
      "end_time": 353161.0,
      "text": "improbable victories"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 353161.0,
      "end_time": 356272.0,
      "text": "by some weak party over someone far stronger."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 356272.0,
      "end_time": 358462.0,
      "text": "Now why do we call David an underdog?"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 358462.0,
      "end_time": 361937.0,
      "text": "Well, we call him an underdog because he&#39;s a kid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 361937.0,
      "end_time": 365473.0,
      "text": "a little kid, and Goliath is this big, strong giant."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 365473.0,
      "end_time": 367128.0,
      "text": "We also call him an underdog"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 367128.0,
      "end_time": 371050.0,
      "text": "because Goliath is an experienced warrior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 371050.0,
      "end_time": 372986.0,
      "text": "and David is just a shepherd."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 372986.0,
      "end_time": 375336.0,
      "text": "But most importantly, we call him an underdog"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 375336.0,
      "end_time": 380346.0,
      "text": "because all he has is -- it&#39;s that Goliath is outfitted with"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 380346.0,
      "end_time": 382351.0,
      "text": "all of this modern weaponry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 382351.0,
      "end_time": 384127.0,
      "text": "this glittering coat of armor"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 384127.0,
      "end_time": 387962.0,
      "text": "and a sword and a javelin and a spear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 387962.0,
      "end_time": 391792.0,
      "text": "and all David has is this sling."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 391792.0,
      "end_time": 393490.0,
      "text": "Well, let&#39;s start there with the phrase"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 393490.0,
      "end_time": 395934.0,
      "text": "&quot;All David has is this sling,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 395934.0,
      "end_time": 398801.0,
      "text": "because that&#39;s the first mistake that we make."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 398801.0,
      "end_time": 402358.0,
      "text": "In ancient warfare, there are three kinds of warriors."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 402358.0,
      "end_time": 405789.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s cavalry, men on horseback and with chariots."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 405789.0,
      "end_time": 408915.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s heavy infantry, which are foot soldiers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 408915.0,
      "end_time": 411805.0,
      "text": "armed foot soldiers with swords and shields"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 411805.0,
      "end_time": 413305.0,
      "text": "and some kind of armor."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 413305.0,
      "end_time": 416533.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s artillery, and artillery are archers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 416533.0,
      "end_time": 418705.0,
      "text": "but, more importantly, slingers."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 418705.0,
      "end_time": 421766.0,
      "text": "And a slinger is someone who has a leather pouch"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 421766.0,
      "end_time": 424563.0,
      "text": "with two long cords attached to it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 424563.0,
      "end_time": 427765.0,
      "text": "and they put a projectile, either a rock or a lead ball,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 427765.0,
      "end_time": 430886.0,
      "text": "inside the pouch, and they whirl it around like this"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 430886.0,
      "end_time": 433529.0,
      "text": "and they let one of the cords go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 433529.0,
      "end_time": 437399.0,
      "text": "and the effect is to send the projectile forward"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 437399.0,
      "end_time": 440704.0,
      "text": "towards its target."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 440704.0,
      "end_time": 443439.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what David has, and it&#39;s important to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 443439.0,
      "end_time": 446286.0,
      "text": "that that sling is not a slingshot."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 446286.0,
      "end_time": 448905.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not this, right? It&#39;s not a child&#39;s toy."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 448905.0,
      "end_time": 452730.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s in fact an incredibly devastating weapon."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 452730.0,
      "end_time": 455706.0,
      "text": "When David rolls it around like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 455706.0,
      "end_time": 458935.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s turning the sling around probably"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 458935.0,
      "end_time": 461607.0,
      "text": "at six or seven revolutions per second,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 461607.0,
      "end_time": 465452.0,
      "text": "and that means that when the rock is released,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 465452.0,
      "end_time": 467652.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s going forward really fast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 467652.0,
      "end_time": 469425.0,
      "text": "probably 35 meters per second."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 469425.0,
      "end_time": 472990.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s substantially faster than a baseball"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 472990.0,
      "end_time": 476623.0,
      "text": "thrown by even the finest of baseball pitchers."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 476623.0,
      "end_time": 480506.0,
      "text": "More than that, the stones in the Valley of Elah"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 480506.0,
      "end_time": 483162.0,
      "text": "were not normal rocks. They were barium sulphate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 483162.0,
      "end_time": 486481.0,
      "text": "which are rocks twice the density of normal stones."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 486481.0,
      "end_time": 489118.0,
      "text": "If you do the calculations on the ballistics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 489118.0,
      "end_time": 493002.0,
      "text": "on the stopping power of the rock fired from David&#39;s sling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 493002.0,
      "end_time": 495323.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s roughly equal to the stopping power"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 495323.0,
      "end_time": 498880.0,
      "text": "of a [.45 caliber] handgun."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 498880.0,
      "end_time": 501874.0,
      "text": "This is an incredibly devastating weapon."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 501874.0,
      "end_time": 506472.0,
      "text": "Accuracy, we know from historical records"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 506472.0,
      "end_time": 510970.0,
      "text": "that slingers -- experienced slingers could hit"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 510970.0,
      "end_time": 516993.0,
      "text": "and maim or even kill a target at distances of up to 200 yards."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 516993.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519963.00000000006,
      "text": "From medieval tapestries, we know that slingers"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 519962.99999999994,
      "end_time": 522320.99999999994,
      "text": "were capable of hitting birds in flight."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 522321.0,
      "end_time": 524755.0,
      "text": "They were incredibly accurate."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 524755.0,
      "end_time": 528312.0,
      "text": "When David lines up -- and he&#39;s not 200 yards away from Goliath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 528312.0,
      "end_time": 529921.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s quite close to Goliath --"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 529921.0,
      "end_time": 533336.0,
      "text": "when he lines up and fires that thing at Goliath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 533336.0,
      "end_time": 536398.0,
      "text": "he has every intention and every expectation"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 536398.0,
      "end_time": 539101.0,
      "text": "of being able to hit Goliath at his most vulnerable spot"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 539101.0,
      "end_time": 540429.0,
      "text": "between his eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 540429.0,
      "end_time": 542445.0,
      "text": "If you go back over the history of ancient warfare,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 542445.0,
      "end_time": 545257.0,
      "text": "you will find time and time again"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 545257.0,
      "end_time": 549260.0,
      "text": "that slingers were the decisive factor against infantry"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 549260.0,
      "end_time": 554285.0,
      "text": "in one kind of battle or another."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 554285.0,
      "end_time": 558181.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s Goliath? He&#39;s heavy infantry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 558181.0,
      "end_time": 563380.0,
      "text": "and his expectation when he challenges the Israelites to a duel"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 563380.0,
      "end_time": 567235.0,
      "text": "is that he&#39;s going to be fighting another heavy infantryman."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 567235.0,
      "end_time": 569406.0,
      "text": "When he says, &quot;Come to me that I might"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 569406.0,
      "end_time": 572358.0,
      "text": "feed your flesh to the birds of the heavens and the beasts of the field,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 572358.0,
      "end_time": 574358.0,
      "text": "the key phrase is &quot;Come to me.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 574358.0,
      "end_time": 576496.0,
      "text": "Come up to me because we&#39;re going to fight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 576496.0,
      "end_time": 578207.0,
      "text": "hand to hand, like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 578207.0,
      "end_time": 580335.0,
      "text": "Saul has the same expectation."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 580335.0,
      "end_time": 582694.0,
      "text": "David says, &quot;I want to fight Goliath,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 582694.0,
      "end_time": 584515.0,
      "text": "and Saul tries to give him his armor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 584515.0,
      "end_time": 587242.0,
      "text": "because Saul is thinking, &quot;Oh, when you say &#39;fight Goliath,&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 587242.0,
      "end_time": 590509.0,
      "text": "you mean &#39;fight him in hand-to-hand combat,&#39;"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 590509.0,
      "end_time": 592697.0,
      "text": "infantry on infantry.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 592697.0,
      "end_time": 595671.0,
      "text": "But David has absolutely no expectation."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 595671.0,
      "end_time": 598222.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s not going to fight him that way. Why would he?"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 598222.0,
      "end_time": 601230.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s a shepherd. He&#39;s spent his entire career"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 601230.0,
      "end_time": 605443.0,
      "text": "using a sling to defend his flock against lions and wolves."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 605443.0,
      "end_time": 607193.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s where his strength lies."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 607193.0,
      "end_time": 609725.0,
      "text": "So here he is, this shepherd, experienced"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 609725.0,
      "end_time": 611764.0,
      "text": "in the use of a devastating weapon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 611764.0,
      "end_time": 614158.0,
      "text": "up against this lumbering giant"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 614158.0,
      "end_time": 617458.0,
      "text": "weighed down by a hundred pounds of armor"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 617458.0,
      "end_time": 618959.0,
      "text": "and these incredibly heavy weapons"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 618959.0,
      "end_time": 622056.0,
      "text": "that are useful only in short-range combat."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 622056.0,
      "end_time": 626793.0,
      "text": "Goliath is a sitting duck. He doesn&#39;t have a chance."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 626793.0,
      "end_time": 629599.0,
      "text": "So why do we keep calling David an underdog,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 629599.0,
      "end_time": 635423.0,
      "text": "and why do we keep referring to his victory as improbable?"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 635423.0,
      "end_time": 638263.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a second piece of this that&#39;s important."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 638263.0,
      "end_time": 641661.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not just that we misunderstand David"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 641661.0,
      "end_time": 643566.0,
      "text": "and his choice of weaponry."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 643566.0,
      "end_time": 646905.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also that we profoundly misunderstand Goliath."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 646905.0,
      "end_time": 650139.0,
      "text": "Goliath is not what he seems to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 650139.0,
      "end_time": 654127.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s all kinds of hints of this in the Biblical text,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 654127.0,
      "end_time": 656932.0,
      "text": "things that are in retrospect quite puzzling"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 656932.0,
      "end_time": 660709.0,
      "text": "and don&#39;t square with his image as this mighty warrior."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 660709.0,
      "end_time": 664086.0,
      "text": "So to begin with, the Bible says that Goliath"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 664086.0,
      "end_time": 668051.0,
      "text": "is led onto the valley floor by an attendant."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 668051.0,
      "end_time": 670260.0,
      "text": "Now that is weird, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 670260.0,
      "end_time": 672390.0,
      "text": "Here is this mighty warrior"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 672390.0,
      "end_time": 675197.0,
      "text": "challenging the Israelites to one-on-one combat."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 675197.0,
      "end_time": 677909.0,
      "text": "Why is he being led by the hand"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 677909.0,
      "end_time": 680959.0,
      "text": "by some young boy, presumably,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 680959.0,
      "end_time": 683421.0,
      "text": "to the point of combat?"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 683421.0,
      "end_time": 687775.0,
      "text": "Secondly, the Bible story makes special note"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 687775.0,
      "end_time": 690864.0,
      "text": "of how slowly Goliath moves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 690864.0,
      "end_time": 692890.0,
      "text": "another odd thing to say when you&#39;re describing"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 692890.0,
      "end_time": 696940.0,
      "text": "the mightiest warrior known to man at that point."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 696940.0,
      "end_time": 698763.0,
      "text": "And then there&#39;s this whole weird thing"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 698763.0,
      "end_time": 702575.0,
      "text": "about how long it takes Goliath to react"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 702575.0,
      "end_time": 704571.0,
      "text": "to the sight of David."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 704571.0,
      "end_time": 707349.0,
      "text": "So David&#39;s coming down the mountain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 707349.0,
      "end_time": 711286.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;s clearly not preparing for hand-to-hand combat."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 711286.0,
      "end_time": 713254.0,
      "text": "There is nothing about him that says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 713254.0,
      "end_time": 715288.0,
      "text": "&quot;I am about to fight you like this.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 715288.0,
      "end_time": 717019.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s not even carrying a sword."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 717019.0,
      "end_time": 719701.0,
      "text": "Why does Goliath not react to that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 719701.0,
      "end_time": 723929.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s as if he&#39;s oblivious to what&#39;s going on that day."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 723929.0,
      "end_time": 727876.0,
      "text": "And then there&#39;s that strange comment he makes to David:"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 727876.0,
      "end_time": 732171.0,
      "text": "&quot;Am I a dog that you should come to me with sticks?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 732171.0,
      "end_time": 735994.0,
      "text": "Sticks? David only has one stick."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 735994.0,
      "end_time": 738253.0,
      "text": "Well, it turns out that there&#39;s been a great deal"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 738253.0,
      "end_time": 741294.0,
      "text": "of speculation within the medical community over the years"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 741294.0,
      "end_time": 743820.0,
      "text": "about whether there is something"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 743820.0,
      "end_time": 746709.0,
      "text": "fundamentally wrong with Goliath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 746709.0,
      "end_time": 750118.0,
      "text": "an attempt to make sense of all of those apparent anomalies."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 750118.0,
      "end_time": 751280.0,
      "text": "There have been many articles written."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 751280.0,
      "end_time": 755274.0,
      "text": "The first one was in 1960 in the Indiana Medical Journal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 755274.0,
      "end_time": 757629.0,
      "text": "and it started a chain of speculation"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 757629.0,
      "end_time": 760752.0,
      "text": "that starts with an explanation for Goliath&#39;s height."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 760752.0,
      "end_time": 763675.0,
      "text": "So Goliath is head and shoulders above"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 763675.0,
      "end_time": 765837.0,
      "text": "all of his peers in that era,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 765837.0,
      "end_time": 769819.0,
      "text": "and usually when someone is that far out of the norm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 769819.0,
      "end_time": 771416.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s an explanation for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 771416.0,
      "end_time": 774649.0,
      "text": "So the most common form of giantism"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 774649.0,
      "end_time": 777384.0,
      "text": "is a condition called acromegaly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 777384.0,
      "end_time": 780287.0,
      "text": "and acromegaly is caused by a benign tumor"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 780287.0,
      "end_time": 782790.0,
      "text": "on your pituitary gland"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 782790.0,
      "end_time": 785506.0,
      "text": "that causes an overproduction of human growth hormone."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 785506.0,
      "end_time": 789065.0,
      "text": "And throughout history, many of the most famous giants"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 789065.0,
      "end_time": 790834.0,
      "text": "have all had acromegaly."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 790834.0,
      "end_time": 792898.0,
      "text": "So the tallest person of all time"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 792898.0,
      "end_time": 794465.0,
      "text": "was a guy named Robert Wadlow"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 794465.0,
      "end_time": 797516.0,
      "text": "who was still growing when he died at the age of 24"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 797516.0,
      "end_time": 800405.0,
      "text": "and he was 8 foot 11."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 800405.0,
      "end_time": 801819.0,
      "text": "He had acromegaly."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 801819.0,
      "end_time": 804354.0,
      "text": "Do you remember the wrestler André the Giant?"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 804354.0,
      "end_time": 806037.0,
      "text": "Famous. He had acromegaly."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 806037.0,
      "end_time": 810576.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s even speculation that Abraham Lincoln had acromegaly."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 810576.0,
      "end_time": 811654.0,
      "text": "Anyone who&#39;s unusually tall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 811654.0,
      "end_time": 814407.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s the first explanation we come up with."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 814407.0,
      "end_time": 818402.0,
      "text": "And acromegaly has a very distinct set of side effects"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 818402.0,
      "end_time": 819627.0,
      "text": "associated with it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 819627.0,
      "end_time": 823189.0,
      "text": "principally having to do with vision."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 823189.0,
      "end_time": 826485.0,
      "text": "The pituitary tumor, as it grows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 826485.0,
      "end_time": 830533.0,
      "text": "often starts to compress the visual nerves in your brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 830533.0,
      "end_time": 833037.0,
      "text": "with the result that people with acromegaly"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 833037.0,
      "end_time": 838508.0,
      "text": "have either double vision or they are profoundly nearsighted."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 838508.0,
      "end_time": 841101.0,
      "text": "So when people have started to speculate"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 841101.0,
      "end_time": 844332.0,
      "text": "about what might have been wrong with Goliath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 844332.0,
      "end_time": 845243.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve said, &quot;Wait a minute,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 845243.0,
      "end_time": 848433.0,
      "text": "he looks and sounds an awful lot like someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 848433.0,
      "end_time": 850006.0,
      "text": "who has acromegaly.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 850006.0,
      "end_time": 852990.0,
      "text": "And that would also explain so much of what was strange"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 852990.0,
      "end_time": 855117.0,
      "text": "about his behavior that day."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 855117.0,
      "end_time": 856938.0,
      "text": "Why does he move so slowly"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 856938.0,
      "end_time": 860466.0,
      "text": "and have to be escorted down into the valley floor"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 860466.0,
      "end_time": 861825.0,
      "text": "by an attendant?"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 861825.0,
      "end_time": 864813.0,
      "text": "Because he can&#39;t make his way on his own."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 864813.0,
      "end_time": 868070.0,
      "text": "Why is he so strangely oblivious to David"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 868070.0,
      "end_time": 870719.0,
      "text": "that he doesn&#39;t understand that David&#39;s not going to fight him"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 870719.0,
      "end_time": 872866.0,
      "text": "until the very last moment?"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 872866.0,
      "end_time": 875375.0,
      "text": "Because he can&#39;t see him."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 875375.0,
      "end_time": 878692.0,
      "text": "When he says, &quot;Come to me that I might feed your flesh"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 878692.0,
      "end_time": 881188.0,
      "text": "to the birds of the heavens and the beasts of the field,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 881188.0,
      "end_time": 885832.0,
      "text": "the phrase &quot;come to me&quot; is a hint also of his vulnerability."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 885832.0,
      "end_time": 888816.0,
      "text": "Come to me because I can&#39;t see you."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 888816.0,
      "end_time": 894030.0,
      "text": "And then there&#39;s, &quot;Am I a dog that you should come to me with sticks?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 894030.0,
      "end_time": 899360.0,
      "text": "He sees two sticks when David has only one."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 899360.0,
      "end_time": 902324.0,
      "text": "So the Israelites up on the mountain ridge"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 902324.0,
      "end_time": 904521.0,
      "text": "looking down on him thought he was"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 904521.0,
      "end_time": 907632.0,
      "text": "this extraordinarily powerful foe."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 907632.0,
      "end_time": 909608.0,
      "text": "What they didn&#39;t understand was that"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 909608.0,
      "end_time": 912905.0,
      "text": "the very thing that was the source of his apparent strength"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 912905.0,
      "end_time": 916660.0,
      "text": "was also the source of his greatest weakness."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 916660.0,
      "end_time": 918617.0,
      "text": "And there is, I think, in that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 918617.0,
      "end_time": 921822.0,
      "text": "a very important lesson for all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 921822.0,
      "end_time": 925684.0,
      "text": "Giants are not as strong and powerful as they seem."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 925684.0,
      "end_time": 929173.0,
      "text": "And sometimes the shepherd boy has a sling in his pocket."
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 929173.0,
      "end_time": 930960.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 930960.0,
      "end_time": 940960.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}